00:00:14.729 --> 00:00:16.436
he asked the students how much time

00:00:16.436 --> 00:00:18.978
they spent completing their projects.

00:00:18.978 --> 00:00:20.975
Create a bar graph to show how much time

00:00:20.975 --> 00:00:24.632
