00:01:37.731 --> 00:01:39.856
So let's do a couple more of these.

00:01:39.856 --> 00:01:43.002
All right, so now it tells
us Rose's flower shop

00:01:43.002 --> 00:01:45.475
makes bouquets for special occasions.

00:01:45.475 --> 00:01:46.612
Each bouquet comes with

00:01:46.612 --> 00:01:48.400
a different number of flowers.

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:50.699
Create a picture graph to show the number

00:01:50.699 --> 00:01:51.976
of flowers in each bouquet.

00:01:51.976 --> 00:01:53.659
So this is kind of like a bar graph,

00:01:53.659 --> 00:01:55.181
but instead we're gonna use pictures.

00:01:55.181 --> 00:01:57.513
Each picture shows a certain number.

00:01:57.513 --> 00:01:59.151
So in this case, a picture of a flower

00:01:59.151 --> 00:02:01.170
represents three flowers.

00:02:01.170 --> 00:02:05.988
So the Mother's day
bouquet has 21 flowers.

00:02:05.988 --> 00:02:07.892
So 21 flowers.

00:02:07.892 --> 00:02:11.107
Now you might be tempted
to put 21 pictures

00:02:11.107 --> 00:02:13.186
of flowers here, but you have to remember

00:02:13.186 --> 00:02:16.506
each of these flowers
represent three flowers.

00:02:16.506 --> 00:02:17.388
So one way to think about it,

00:02:17.388 --> 00:02:18.890
you could count by threes.

00:02:18.890 --> 00:02:21.612
Three, six, nine,

00:02:21.633 --> 00:02:26.211
12, 15, 18, 21.

00:02:26.211 --> 00:02:27.836
So that over here, this right over here,

00:02:27.836 --> 00:02:29.429
would represent 21 flowers.

00:02:29.429 --> 00:02:33.145
And you notice I just made
seven of this picture,

00:02:33.145 --> 00:02:34.769
and that makes sense because seven

00:02:34.769 --> 00:02:36.267
of these pictures, and
each of these pictures

00:02:36.267 --> 00:02:39.761
represent three flowers,
seven times three is 21.

00:02:39.761 --> 00:02:43.942
The Mother's Day bouquet
has 21 flowers in it.

00:02:43.942 --> 00:02:46.727
All right, the Anniversary
bouquet has 27 flowers.

00:02:46.727 --> 00:02:48.897
So three, six, nine,

00:02:48.897 --> 00:02:53.897
12, 15, 18, 21, 24, 27.

00:02:53.936 --> 00:02:55.189
I have nine flowers here.

00:02:55.189 --> 00:02:58.289
Nine times three is 27.

00:02:58.289 --> 00:03:00.913
The Birthday bouquet has 18.

00:03:00.913 --> 00:03:05.835
So three, six, nine, 12, 15, 18.

00:03:05.835 --> 00:03:07.438
And I just made six pictures here

00:03:07.438 --> 00:03:09.400
because each of them
represent three flowers.

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:12.382
Six times three is 18.

00:03:12.382 --> 00:03:14.217
Then finally, the Congratulations bouquet

00:03:14.217 --> 00:03:15.796
has 12 flowers in it.

00:03:15.796 --> 00:03:20.695
Three, six, nine, and 12.

00:03:20.695 --> 00:03:21.704
There you go.

00:03:21.704 --> 00:03:23.136
I think we're done.

00:03:23.136 --> 00:03:24.913
I think we're done.

