00:03:29.043 --> 00:03:31.945
Barry Bee and his bee friends love

00:03:31.945 --> 00:03:33.744
to pollinate flowers.

00:03:33.744 --> 00:03:35.799
They created a chart and a picture graph

00:03:35.799 --> 00:03:37.088
to show how many flowers each

00:03:37.088 --> 00:03:38.830
of them pollinated today.

00:03:38.830 --> 00:03:40.884
Use the information in the chart

00:03:40.884 --> 00:03:43.658
to answer the question
about the picture graph.

00:03:43.658 --> 00:03:45.566
So it says, On the picture graph,

00:03:45.566 --> 00:03:48.085
each flower equals blank flowers,

00:03:48.085 --> 00:03:50.209
or each picture of a flower, I should say,

00:03:50.209 --> 00:03:52.867
equals a blank number of flowers.

00:03:52.867 --> 00:03:56.121
So it says Barry pollinated 27.

00:03:56.121 --> 00:03:57.330
These are impressive bees

00:03:57.330 --> 00:03:59.025
that they sit there making charts.

00:03:59.025 --> 00:04:03.900
Barry pollinated 27 flowers,

00:04:03.900 --> 00:04:05.607
and they only drew three pictures here.

00:04:05.607 --> 00:04:10.285
So these three flower
pictures must represent 27.

00:04:10.285 --> 00:04:11.840
So the way that they would represent 27

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:13.664
is if each of these represent nine

00:04:13.664 --> 00:04:17.448
because we'd have nine, 18, 27.

00:04:17.448 --> 00:04:19.700
So each of these must be nine flowers.

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:21.141
But let's see if that works.

00:04:21.141 --> 00:04:23.728
So for Bumbly, 63.

00:04:23.728 --> 00:04:28.338
So let's see, nine, 18, 27,

00:04:28.338 --> 00:04:33.086
36, 45, 54, 63.

00:04:33.086 --> 00:04:34.781
Yep, it looks like it works out.

00:04:34.781 --> 00:04:38.205
Betty is one, two, three, four, five, six.

00:04:38.205 --> 00:04:40.597
Six, six times nine is 54.

00:04:40.597 --> 00:04:43.384
That is the number of
flowers she pollinated.

00:04:43.384 --> 00:04:45.903
Bertie, one, two, three, four, five.

00:04:45.903 --> 00:04:47.980
If each of those pictures represent nine,

00:04:47.980 --> 00:04:50.778
then this would be five times nine is 45.

00:04:50.778 --> 00:04:53.140
That is the number of flowers Bertie

00:04:53.140 --> 00:04:56.170
had actually pollinated.

